  "description": "The Lion's Mane jellyfish has up to 1,200 tendrils. This preset evokes that: six delay lines multiplying into filaments, each with a unique modulation phase offset. The drift is purposeful — each tendril moves at its own rate through the same current. Lush, alive, disorienting at high mod depth.",
